AtomVM is dual-licensed. This project exercises the Apache License 2.0 option.

AtomVM source is used in the following ways:
  - vendor/AtomVM/ contains the full AtomVM source (git submodule)
  - atomvm-wasi/ is a WASI platform adapter that links against libAtomVM
  - priv/atomvm.wasm is the AtomVM virtual machine compiled to WebAssembly
  - priv/stdlib/*.beam are AtomVM standard library modules compiled to BEAM
  - atomvm-wasi/include/nifs_hash.h is generated from AtomVM's nifs.gperf
  - atomvm-wasi/include/bifs_hash.h is generated from AtomVM's bifs.gperf

AtomVM source code is available at: https://github.com/atomvm/AtomVM

